stateDiagram-v2
  %% Diagram 24: AI Cold-Start Bootstrap and Data Quality Lifecycle

  [*] --> Tier1: Onboarding complete

  state Tier1 {
    [*] --> SeedOnly
    SeedOnly: Tier 1\nSeed-only mode\nsynthetic_sales_seed active\nLow-confidence baseline
  }

  Tier1 --> MissingSeed: Seed not submitted
  MissingSeed: Fallback baseline path\nPrompt vendor for seed entry
  MissingSeed --> Tier1: Seed submitted

  Tier1 --> Tier2: Real orders begin (Week 1+)

  state Tier2 {
    [*] --> MixedData
    MixedData: Tier 2\nReal + seed blended\ndata_quality_score rising
  }

  Tier2 --> SparseReal: Real volume remains sparse
  SparseReal: Continue mixed mode\nConfidence constrained
  SparseReal --> Tier2: More real data arrives

  Tier2 --> Tier3: Day 90+ reached

  state Tier3 {
    [*] --> RealOnly
    RealOnly: Tier 3\nSeed deprecated\ndata_quality_score = 1.0
  }

  Tier3 --> [*]
